Venture Building
 Exploring investment, business and collaboration opportunities
 Driving development process from ideation, feasibility studies, prototyping to commercial roll-out
 Assisting in the management of operational aspects of new ventures under the Company
 Networking, liaising and negotiating with the Company뭩 current and potential business partners, assisting in deal closure

Research
 Working closely with management to determine research objectives
 Utilising various professional sources to find and extract pertinent information
