Delightex is a research and venture building arm of a Japanese consumer goods MNC that has the mandate to identify, invest and build business around naturally occurring substances. Company seeks to evaluate technologies, invest and build innovative companies with the capacity to create a massive shift in global consumption habits.
Delightex is seeking like-minded individuals for the role of Venture Builder to identify and create businesses for next generation consumers.

May visit our website at www.delightexplorers.com to find out more.